    <br />
    <br />
    <br />
    <hr>
    <h1 class="text-brand mt-10 flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6">
      Deja Video
      <small class="bg-brand/5 text-[0.8125rem] ml-3 rounded-full px-2 font-medium leading-6">
        v<%= Application.spec(:dejavideo, :vsn) %>
      </small>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-[2rem] mt-4 font-semibold leading-10 tracking-tighter text-zinc-900 text-balance">
      The feeling that you've already watched a video, even though you know you haven't.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-zinc-600">
      Disc Jockey the best videos quickly, with more control and fewer moving parts. Join our growing community of DJs using Deja Video to craft playlists, channels, and more, for fun or at broadcast scale.
    </p>
